<div class="banner">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <h2>love movies?</h2>
    <h1>say hello to <span id="main-title">Holly</span></h1>
    <div class="start-btn">
      <%= link_to "START", '#', class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="hp-wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="hp-content">
          <div class="hp-icon">
            <%= emojify ":clipboard: :movie_camera: :yum:" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-text">
            <h3>Fill you watchlist</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">Holly is a powerful, yet simple, movie watchlist manager:</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>Search and add the movies you want to watch</li>
              <li>Browse your own watchlist (by filtering by duration, stars...)</li>
              <li>Access movies info (overview, cast, trailer, poster...)</li>
              <li>Know how you can watch the film (theaters or streaming)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="hp-content">
          <div class="hp-icon">
            <%= emojify ":mailbox: :e-mail: :grinning:" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-text">
            <h3>Get updates</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">Each week, we'll send you one email, to let you know :</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>which movies are available (theaters or streaming)</li>
              <li>which movies you share with your friends watchlist.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="hp-content">
          <div class="hp-icon">
            <%= emojify ":iphone: :speech_balloon: :astonished:" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-text">
            <h3>On the go</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">For us, Holly is more than a web service. We really want to give it a soul. So now, you can now interact with Holly via Facebook Messenger, whether in your desktop browser, or on the Messenger mobile app. Search a movie, add it, show your watchlist... you can do all this (and many other things to come), just by chatting with it.
            <br>Awesome, right?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>







